# list of glob patterns to be excluded when repacking the vpk
# - use a leading slash anchor the path
# - use a exclamation mark prefix to negate the pattern
# - patterns are scanned from start to end
# - the first matched rule sets the file as excluded unless a negated rule afterwards also matches it
# - no further rules are matched after a negated exclusion

*.vpk
/.vpk*
.nfs*
.directory
.Trash-*
System Volume Information
Thumbs.db
Thumbs.db:encryptable
Desktop.ini
ehthumbs.db
ehthumbs_vista.db
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
.DocumentRevisions-V100
.fseventsd
.Spotlight-V100
.TemporaryItems
.Trashes
.VolumeIcon.icns
.com.apple.timemachine.donotpresent
.vscode
.idea
.git*
.fr-*
[._]*.s[a-v][a-z]
*.swp
*.part
._*
~*
*~
.example_for_negated_rules_*
!.example_for_negated_rules_include_me
